{"tid":2463343,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中概股市值蒸發不斷！傳百度、唯品會和騰訊音樂出現巨量賣單","createTime":"2021-03-26T15:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T16:32:34.000Z","uid":30040,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3d603300cc4bb4ca902d2577d90a28fbc85ec6","tid":2463343,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"來自美國的監管威脅，短短幾天內使中概股市值蒸發數百億美元。周五 (26 日) 美股盤前，消息指出有透過高盛掛出騰訊音樂 (TME-US)、百度(BIDU-US) 和唯品會 (VIPS-US) 的巨量賣單，刺激上述中概股於盤中急挫。<br />\n<br />\n彭博引述知情人士透露，高盛共掛出 5000 萬股的騰訊音樂賣單、3200 萬股唯品會賣單，以及 1000 萬股百度賣單。<br />\n<br />\n三者開盤雖一度轉漲，隨後跌勢加劇。截稿前，騰訊音樂跌超 10%，暫報 18.30 美元；百度跌逾 6%，暫報 190.94 美元；唯品會跌近 6%，暫報 30.14 美元。<br />\n<br />\n美國證券交易委員會 (SEC) 日前宣布準備執行「外國公司問責法案」(HFCA)，要求在美上市外國公司必須遵循美國審計標準，否則將予以下市。該項法案由前總統川普於任期內通過。<br />\n<br />\n除了美國監管措施帶來的不確定性，隨著北京政府日益加強對科技公司的控制，中概股在國內也面臨潛在挑戰。<br />\n<br />\nCNBC 根據 Refinitiv Eikon 數據進行計算得出，截至周五港股收盤，短短三天內熱門中概股的市值急速蒸發。阿里巴巴、百度、京東和網易四家在美上市中概股的市值蒸發近 4700 億港元 (約 600 多億美元)。"},{"pid":"6be8a473549e2a7192e6a71fc0565ad3271636f0","tid":2463343,"uid":394448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:24:21.000Z","msg":"日日跌10% 跌到驚 聽日宣布退市"},{"pid":"3561e9d08d6d58ca0e63a8e23ac02d99a4485b88","tid":2463343,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"百度跌到無力回天咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c9d1339bd90d67f3a22023aef5a108dcb24f1b","tid":2463343,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34956d8fc141a32fb2e285102a4620b316ef8cbb","tid":2463343,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:42:40.000Z","msg":"唔走變廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aedd761571ec7871937a6a4af03335d90f7e748","tid":2463343,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"NIO put賺到笑，早知買多d"},{"pid":"7d45d136b24c2ebe946cff7a4243422a66e6f50b","tid":2463343,"uid":174084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"一有唱淡新聞<br />\n必然大升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99c52ad21a14ea73de326a8f5896d6e4ae977cd","tid":2463343,"uid":28641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3561e9d08d6d58ca0e63a8e23ac02d99a4485b88","tid":2463343,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"百度跌到無力回天咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾技術<br />\n係On9先真係信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4805877e3fcbb4e082e586f9f3a8cc27c1728806","tid":2463343,"uid":387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:32:34.000Z","msg":"其實bidu受到麵神祝福 唔死都難"}]}